OL,2,W+.-'"-$/*%*%*%/"-$/*%Q,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,3,GUK long range forecast
OL,4,
OL,5,COutlook for Wed 29 Jul to Fri 7 AugFDry
OL,6,Fat first across the south with long
OL,7,Fsunny periods, where it will also be
OL,8,Fvery warm. Cloudier in the north with
OL,9,Fsome outbreaks of rain, which could be
OL,10,Fheavy in places, and temperatures
OL,11,Fnearer normal. It will probably become
OL,12,Fmore changeable thereafter, with
OL,13,Fpotential for an area of low pressure
OL,14,Fto move close to or across the UK at
OL,15,Fthe end of July or early August. This
OL,16,Fcould bring spells of heavy rain and
OL,17,Fperhaps some strong winds for a time.
OL,18,FIt may become more settled again
OL,19,Ftoward the end of the first week of
OL,20,FAugust.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
OL,24,ANext Page  BWeather  CReg News  FReg TV
