OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F163A1784906303
OL,1,Wj5hw1~{4k7juhw1{$             G2/2
OL,2,W+.-'"-$/*%*%*%/"-$/*%Q,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,3,GUK long range forecast
OL,4,
OL,5,COutlook for Sat 8 Aug to Sat 22 AugFDry
OL,6,Fand settled conditions will probably
OL,7,Fdominate much of this period with high
OL,8,Fpressure patterns tending to affect
OL,9,Fthe UK. This may be interrupted at
OL,10,Ftimes by Atlantic frontal systems,
OL,11,Fespecially in the north, or
OL,12,Fthunderstorms in the south. However,
OL,13,Foverall rainfall amounts will likely
OL,14,Fbe below normal. Temperatures will
OL,15,Fprobably be above normal and some
OL,16,Fspells of hot weather and heatwaves
OL,17,Fare possible, especially in the south.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
